      "para_id": "Q001002.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) For Annunītum , his spouse , Šu-Suen , the beloved of Enlil , the king whom Enlil chose with the love of his heart , the powerful king , king of Urim , king of the four quarters , built her temple ."
    }
